(45, 1, 'Junior C# ASP.Net developer', 'NetMatch as employer:\r\n- NetMatch is the European market leader in Tourism Internet Software Solutions. We assists travel companies in selling their products online. \r\n- NetMatch provides essential (dedicated side-by-side) training and we encourage candidates in getting an MCSD certificate.\r\n\r\n\r\nCandidate profile: \r\n* You have a IT software related University diploma or comparable;\r\n* You have knowledge of C# and ASP.NET;\r\n* You have knowledge of object orientated programming and designing with UML;\r\n* You have knowledge of XML applications like XHTML, XSIT, XPATH and XML scheme.\r\n* You have a strong personality and can handle stress. You are accurate in work in structure, and you react quickly and flexible to ad-hoc situations. \r\n', 'Trimite CV la email la :jobs@netmatch.ro ', 'NetMatch SRL', 'Cluj-Napoca ', 1, '2007-12-15 12:00:00', '', '2008-01-06 07:21:40', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(46, 1, 'NET developers & Senior .NET developers ', 'IDEAL CANDIDATE:\r\n\r\nProfile:\r\n- You have an IT software related University diploma or you are a student of a related University.\r\n- You have experience working with the Microsoft .NET Framework;\r\n- You have knowledge of object orientated analysis and designing with UML;\r\n- You have worked with XML languages like XHTML, XSLT, XPATH and XML schema.\r\n- A relevant Microsoft certificate (MCSD or MCAD) is a plus.\r\n\r\nJOB RESPONSIBILITIES / BENEFITS:\r\n\r\nYou are responsible for the release of the newest versions of websites and services of travel organizations internationally. You translate a wish into a solution. You seek and discover new techniques. You document designs and code carefully with UML. Grow with the company and make a real impact in shaping both your and the companyâ€™s future.\r\n\r\nYou are responsible for quality, without losing track of development speed. You coach your colleagues on the newest internet technology that you know by heart and you happily share your knowledge with others.\r\n\r\nNetMatch as employer:\r\n- Offers candidates a great chance to develop skills, working with a team of highly motivated and talented Romanian and Dutch software developers using the latest technologies such as .NET, XML, XSLT, etc.\r\n- NetMatch provides essential (dedicated side-by-side) training and we encourage candidates in getting an MCSD certificate.\r\n- Offers an exciting opportunity to work abroad (temporarily or for a longer time) in the Netherlands, so travel is a possibility.\r\n- Competitive salaries and benefits (500 - 1500 Euro)\r\n\r\nCOMPANY OR JOB DESCRIPTION:\r\n\r\nNetMatch assists travel companies in selling their products online. For this NetMatch has developed a .NET application named TourWeb. Our biggest client group currently consists of tour operators that sell their products online with TourWeb. http://www.netmatch.nl/downloads/tourweb2006EN.pdf\r\n\r\nNetMatch is the European market leader in Tourism Internet Software Solutions.\r\n\r\nwww.netmatch.ro\r\nwww.netmatch.nl \r\n', 'Trimite CV la email: jobs@netmatch.ro ', 'NetMatch SRL', 'Cluj-Napoca ', 0, '2007-12-15 12:00:00', '', '2009-04-02 23:43:09', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47, 1, 'C++ Programmers', 'Top software company, with over 1,200 customers in 120 countries, among them 49 of the world''s top 50 banks, is expanding its treasury & capital markets branch in Bucharest. Here we are creating one of the most important development centers of the company, with top specialists working on sophisticated products. \r\n\r\nAt the very heart of the financial software industry, you will be able to achieve exponential career growth, have access to professional training programs and be highly rewarded for your efforts. \r\n\r\nWe believe that everything starts with talent. \r\n\r\nTo learn more about Misys, please log on to www.misys.com \r\n\r\nRequirements: \r\n- University degree: Computer Science, Mathematics, Business IT (ASE) \r\n- Very good knowledge of C, C++ and/or C# \r\n- Knowledge of .NET, Java, Perl, RDBMS appreciated \r\n- Real-time and Distributed Processing appreciated \r\n- Good English knowledge \r\n- Interest in finance \r\n- Commitment, stability, responsibility \r\n- Ability to work independently as well as being a team player \r\n- Excellent verbal and written communication skills \r\n- Time management skills and the ability to work under tight time constraints \r\n- Ability to multi-task between multiple activities \r\n\r\nResponsibilities: \r\n- Develop new financial applications and improve existing modules \r\n- Perform unit testing \r\n- Write technical specifications \r\n- Provide maintenance for existing projects \r\n- Investigate technical and functional defects and propose adequate solutions \r\n- Provide product-related and domain specific consultancy \r\n- Write documentation \r\n- Learn new IT and finance skills, as required \r\n- Travel and direct interaction with client may be required \r\n\r\nBenefits: \r\n- Motivating salary and bonuses, according to results \r\n- Opportunity to develop software projects in a professional environment \r\n- Access to high-end technology \r\n\r\n\r\n', 'If you''re interested in becoming a part of our team of professionals, please send your CVs at mariana.pascu@misys.com , and we''ll be happy to schedule a meeting. ', 'MISYS International Financial Systems', 'Bucuresti ', 0, '2007-12-15 12:00:00', '', '2009-04-02 23:43:09', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(48, 1, 'Aplication Manager', 'Descrierea jobului: \r\n- Asigura analiza, proiectarea, programarea si implementarea de solutii software; \r\n- Asigura mentenanta si suport pentru sistemul informatic; \r\n- Asigura dezvoltarea si mentenanta programelor software integrate cu sistemul informatic. \r\n\r\nCerinte: \r\n- Studii superioare cu specializare in informatica; \r\n- Cunostinte solide MS SQL - administrare, proiectare, programare; \r\n- Capacitate de a asimila rapid noi cunostinte; \r\n- Spirit de echipa. \r\n\r\nConstituie avantaj: \r\n- Cunosterea unui limbaj de programare ( preferabil promovat de Microsoft ); \r\n- Cunostinte ERP iSCALA; \r\n- Experienta minim 1 an intr-o pozitie similara. \r\n', 'trimite CV la e-mail: hr@rhs.ro ', 'RHS COMPANY', 'Bucuresti ', 0, '2007-12-15 12:00:00', '', '2009-04-02 23:43:09', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(49, 1, 'Programator Flash + PHP', 'CANDIDATUL IDEAL: \r\n\r\nProgramator cu inclinatie artistica (sa inteleaga si sa dezvolte ideile directorului de creatie), nivel mediu ActionScripting, cu dorinta continua de dezvoltare, inventiv. \r\n\r\nRESPONSABILITATI \r\n\r\n- dezvoltarea modulelor Flash pentru site-uri (headere, micro-module de calcul, etc) sau chiar a site-urilor integral Flash) \r\n- dezvoltarea bannerelor rich-media, optimizare, integrare sunet si video \r\n- dezvoltarea mini-jocurilor Flash \r\n- transpunerea dinamica a viziunii directorului de creatie \r\n\r\nCERINTE: \r\n\r\n- Integrare grafica in mediul Flash (site web, bannere, aplicatii stand-alone pentru CD) \r\n- Integrare Flash cu XML/PHP/MySQL \r\n\r\nNIVEL: mediu. \r\n\r\nOFERTA (BONUSURI, BENEFICII): \r\n\r\nSe acorda pachet salarial motivant (salariu de baza + bonus progresiv) in functie de performanta. Proiecte interesante cu clienti la fel de interesanti (vezi portfolio-ul partial al agentiei). Integrarea intr-o echipa cu experienta in dezvoltarea de proiecte atit on-line cat si off-line. \r\n\r\nDESCRIEREA COMPANIEI: \r\n\r\nThe Adgency este o agentie de creatie si design interactiv, consultanta de brand si comunicare integrala, fondata Ã®n 2004, cu capital exclusiv romanesc. Din 2006 The Adgency este certificata ISO 9001. \r\n', 'Trimite CV la office@theadgency.ro ', 'The Adgency', 'Bucuresti ', 1, '2007-12-15 12:00:00', '', '2008-01-06 07:21:40', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(50, 1, 'Java Developer', 'Coena is a product development company that specializes in developing state-of-the-art supply chain products.\r\n\r\nWe use techniques from distributed technologies, artificial intelligence, model-driven architecture, and object-oriented technology.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for motivated and quality-driven software professionals to start work on our products in our office in Romania (Cluj-Napoca).\r\n\r\nEligible candidates must meet the following requirements:\r\n- Bachelor''s degree in Computer Science from a recognized University.\r\n- At least 2 years working experience.\r\n- Applicable candidates must demonstrate strong commitment to learning and delivering high quality code.\r\n- Thorough and demonstrable knowledge of Object-Oriented Analysis and Design.\r\n- AJAX-based frameworks, J2EE/Distributed Enterprise Technologies, Domain-driven development.\r\n- Should be fluent in English and have good communication skills.\r\n\r\nWe offer competitive salaries, and an excellent career growth path in leading technologies. \r\n', 'Eligible candidates must provide their Curriculum Vitae (CV) in English to recruitment@coena.ro . Selected candidates will be contacted for a face-to-face interview in Cluj-Napoca. ', 'Coena SRL', 'Cluj-Napoca ', 1, '2007-12-15 12:00:00', '', '2008-01-06 07:21:40', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(51, 1, 'Front-End Web Developer', 'F5 Solutions cauta un Front-End Web Developer care sa raspunda afirmativ la cel putin 5 din urmatoarele 8 intrebari:\r\n\r\n1) Poti face o comparatie intre cel putin 2 framework-uri JavaScript ?\r\n2) Codul XHTML scris de tine este corect din punct de vedere semantic ?\r\n3) Preferi un editor de tip TEXT (cu sintax-highlighting) in detrimentul unui editor de tip WYSIWYG ?\r\n4) Cunosti cel putin o solutie pentru realizarea unui transfer asincron de date cross-domain ?\r\n5) Obisnuiesti sa validezi codul XHTML / CSS conform standardelor W3C ?\r\n6) "Cross-Browser", "fiabilitate" si "scalabilitate" se numara printre caracteristicile definitorii ale proiectelor tale ?\r\n7) Esti familiar cu cel putin 4 dintre urmatorii termeni: "hasLayout", "mostenire", "DOM", "elemente multi-class", "polimorfism" ?\r\n8) Ai folosit pana acum o tehnologie text-based de serializare / transmitere a datelor in afara de XML ?\r\n\r\nCunostintele si conditiile obligatorii sunt urmatoarele:\r\n\r\n- XHTML, CSS;\r\n- XML, XSLT, JSON;\r\n- JavaScript (OOP, minim 4 luni experienta in utilizarea unui framework);\r\n- Un portofoliu care sa cuprinda cel putin 3 proiecte / experimente / aplicatii relevante;\r\n- Seriozitate, responsabilitate, etica profesionala;\r\n- Simtul umorului (nu glumim).\r\n\r\nEsti avantajat daca:\r\n\r\n- Ai experienta in utilizarea Smarty;\r\n- Ai experienta in utilizarea Fireworks si/sau Photoshop (slicing / export);\r\n- Esti familiar cu modul de functionare al tehnologiilor server-side (cel putin la nivel de concept);\r\n- Te implici, esti activ si stii sa-ti exprimi / argumentezi propriile idei si convingeri;\r\n- Esti intr-un proces continuu de autodepasire.\r\n\r\nBeneficii:\r\n\r\n- Proiecte complexe si incitante;\r\n- Pachet salarial si bonusuri atractive;\r\n- Programul (flexibil) incepe undeva in jurul orei 11:00 (somn++, trafic--);\r\n- Atmosfera placuta si degajata;\r\n- Sansa de a te "razbuna" zilnic pe colegii utilizand "