(55, 1, 'Software Devlopers & Telecom Engineers', '1) User Interface Developers\r\n\r\nRequired skills:\r\n- Linux basics\r\n- C & standard library\r\n- Basic GNU development tools (gcc, make, autotools, etc.)\r\n- GTK+\r\n- GUI builders (Glade, Gazpacho, libglade, GTKbuilder)\r\n\r\nExtra skills:\r\n- GObject & ability to create custom widgets\r\n- Theming with gtkrc\r\n- OpenGL (ES version), EDJE and Cairo. Also knowing clutter would be beneficial\r\n\r\n2) Application Developers (Linux/Windows)\r\n\r\nRequired skills:\r\n- Linux basics\r\n- C & standard library\r\n- Basic GNU development tools (gcc, make, autotools, etc.)\r\n- Experience of Linux programming API (threads, IPC, I/O, sockets)\r\n- Glib (data structures, basic types)\r\n\r\nExtra skills:\r\n- Libtool & building shared libraries\r\n- Knowledge of GNOME/freedesktop.org architecture components\r\n- e.g. D-BUS, gconf, GnomeVFS\r\n\r\n3) Telecom/SS7/GSM Engineers\r\n\r\nMandatory:\r\n- Availability to intensive travel abroad\r\n- Work experience in telecom domain\r\n- Experience with Unix (Solaris of HP-UX) server-side system, administration tools and shell scripting\r\n- Knowledge of Oracle\r\n- Excellent verbal and written communication, problem solving and analytical skill\r\n\r\nWill be an advantage:\r\n- Hands-on experience in developing call-processing and messaging applications in GSM/GPRS\r\n- Thorough knowledge of MAP, ISUP, IN, CAMEL, Network Elements such as HLR, VLR, SMSC, GMSC\r\n\r\n4) Embedded Software Developers\r\n\r\n- 3+ years C/C++ languages experience\r\n- 1+ year experience with embedded systems, on-chip debuggers\r\n- Knowledge of OS fundamentals, RTOS\r\n- Knowledge of device drivers, BSP, HW architectures\r\n- Software configuration management (CVS, Clearcase)\r\n\r\nWill be an advantage:\r\n- Experience with ARM processors\r\n- Experience in board design/testing \r\n', 'Feel free to send your resume at: office@altdev.ro ', 'AltDev', 'Bucuresti ', 1, '2007-12-15 12:00:00', '', '2008-01-06 07:21:40', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(56, 1, 'Programator ASP.NET si SQL Server', 'CANDIDATUL IDEAL:\r\n\r\n- cunostinte foarte bune baze de date relationale (MS SQL Server)\r\n- cunostinte foarte bune ASP.NET, XML, JavaScript\r\n- minim 2 ani experienta\r\n- Abilitati de comunicare\r\n\r\n\r\nRESPONSABILITATI / BENEFICII:\r\n\r\nRolul principal pentru acest post este de a programa in ASP.Net si SQL Server 2000/2005, de a identifica solutii de optimizare si de scalare pentru o serie de aplicatii complexe, de mari dimensiuni.\r\nVor fi considerati pentru interviu doar candidatii cu experienta demonstrabila in .Net. Sunt de asemenea necesare cunostinte solide de SQL.\r\nNivelul minim de educatie este licenta in informatica (Matematica, Automatica, Cibernetica). Candidatii pot fi si studenti in ani terminali la facultatile amintite. \r\n\r\n', 'AplicÄƒ on-line la www.boom.ro/jobs ', 'NetBridge Investments', 'BucureÅŸti ', 1, '2007-12-15 12:00:00', '', '2008-01-06 07:21:40', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
