(65, 1, 'SENIOR TESTER', 'Essential skills:\r\n\r\nâ€¢Good experience in functional testing;\r\nâ€¢Good knowledge of the software testing lifecycle;\r\nâ€¢Strong analytical and organizational skills; attention to details;\r\nâ€¢Ability to understand business processes;\r\nâ€¢Strong English language skills (both oral and written).\r\n\r\nDesirable skills:\r\n\r\nâ€¢Skills in using Mercury Test Director\r\nâ€¢Experience/knowledge of telecom-specific CRM and billing systems\r\nâ€¢Wide use of test tools\r\n\r\nRESPONSABILITATI / BENEFICII:\r\n\r\nProject description\r\n\r\nWeâ€™re providing high-quality software testing services to one of the largest mobile telecommunications network companies in the world. Our main responsibilities consist in performing software testing throughout the whole system and system integration testing lifecycle for various CRM, Billing and Self-Care applications.\r\n\r\n\r\nYou will be required to:\r\n\r\nâ€¢Review and analyze documentation/specifications;\r\nâ€¢Contribute to the creation of test plans;\r\nâ€¢Identify, write and peer review test cases based on the specifications;\r\nâ€¢Identify and create test data;\r\nâ€¢Run, execute tests according to plan;\r\nâ€¢Identify and report defects; track and retest defects;\r\nâ€¢Provide constructive criticism; contribute to lessons learnt for future releases and projects. \r\n', 'Email luci.savu@endava.com ', 'ENDAVA', 'Cluj-Napoca ', 1, '2007-12-15 12:00:00', '', '2009-04-11 09:16:31', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
