(67, 1, 'Security Software Tester and Supporter', 'Acunetix is an international software company specializing in web security scanning software. Web attacks are on the rise and traditional network security does not protect against them. Acunetix developed a Media Vulnerability Scanner that crawls a website and checks for vulnerabilities in web applications which often have a direct line into the company''s most valuable data assets. The Acunetix management team is backed by many years of experience in marketing and selling security software. Being a young, dynamic and growing company you will be assured of an exciting job opportunity with excellent career prospects.\r\n\r\nThis position requires extensive experience with software testing and knowledge of computer security software.\r\n\r\nYou will be in charge of handling support issues for customers worldwide whilst also coordinating and testing product releases. In addition, you will be required to write technical documentation and white papers, as well as track security blogs worldwide.\r\n\r\nYou will need to relocate to Cluj-Napoca.\r\n\r\nYou should have a good command of English language.\r\n\r\n', 'Trimite CV la email info@acunetix.com ', 'Acunetix ', 'Cluj Napoca', 1, '2007-12-15 12:00:00', '', '2009-04-11 09:16:31', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(68, 1, 'Technical HelpDesk Assistant', 'Cautam persoane tinere, dinamice (disponibilitate de a calatori in tara sau in afara cca. 30% din timp), cu cunostinte medii de engleza sau franceza, pentru un client cu traditie in domeniul dezvoltarii de solutii expert in HR. \r\nCandidatul ideal trebuie sa aiba experienta in domeniul HelpDesk de cel putin 2 ani, cunostinte medii de administrare servere (MS SQL, MS Exchange, Active Directory), abilitati de comunicare si analiza peste medie si sa fie dispus sa se deplaseze (cand este cazul) la sediile clientilor pentru supervizarea proceselor de implementare / configurare / depanare a sistemelor dezvoltate de clientul nostru. \r\nOferim posibilitatea de a participa intr-un mediu dinamic, international, cu reale posibilitati de afirmare. \r\nVa rugam sa trimiteti CV-ul la bogdan@bobyte.ro , insotit de pretentiile salariale. Numai persoanele potrivite vor fi contactate', 'Trimiteti CV-ul la bogdan@bobyte.ro ', 'boBYTE Consulting', 'Bucuresti ', 1, '2007-12-15 12:00:00', '', '2009-04-11 09:16:31', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
