(77, 1, 'Software Quality Engineer', 'Position Purpose:\r\n• We are looking for a dedicated, self motivated, highly skilled Software Quality Engineer to join our team for building high-end, highly scalable Web and transactional applications.\r\n• Successful candidates will have a solid Quality Assurance &amp; Development background (Java, NET, C++, Flash) with the ability and passion to ensure development codebases are of high quality.\r\n• Knowledge of automated test tools.\r\n• BSc in Computer Science or equivalent demonstrated knowledge\r\n• Understanding of browser compatibility issues\r\n• Proficiency in test case generation techniques: equivalence partitioning, boundary value analysis etc\r\n• Experience of different software development methods\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n• Work as integral part of the development teams to ensure codebase is of the highest quality\r\n• Help developers to work within a test driven development environment\r\n• Ensure test suite is comprehensive, automated and repeatable\r\n• Maintain continuous integration system\r\n• Ensure end to end integration tests are run nightly\r\n• Work with Product Owner to ensure that the business and operational requirements have valid, automated, tests\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAbout Xoomworks\r\n\r\nXoomworks is a professional services company focused on application, integration and managed services. Some areas that we cover are eGaming, Procurement, Spend Management and Finance.\r\n\r\nXoomworks was founded in 2000 by former partners of Deloitte Consulting who wanted to introduce a new style of IT services partner, combining the business consulting with technical consulting in order to successfully deliver solutions to large and mid-sized companies.\r\n\r\nCulturally we combine the technical and business expertise of a Big 4 consultancy with the ethos and innovation of a small business.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for people who are interested in working with the latest hardware, latest technologies and latest development processes on mission critical application. We care about our employees and we invest in them.', 'If interested please send an English version of your resume to pdro@xoomworks.com', 'SC Xoomworks Ro SRL', 'Cluj-Napoca', 1, '2007-12-27 12:00:00', '', '2009-04-11 09:16:31', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
